Favicon - ‚ÄúSL‚Äù Logo
Download: SVG | PNG | PDF
Bold, readable ‚ÄúSL‚Äù favicon with brand gradient - perfect visibility at all sizes.


Show SVG code

&lt;svg viewBox="0 0 100 100" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"&gt;
  &lt;title&gt;Sustainability Lab - SL Favicon&lt;/title&gt;
  &lt;defs&gt;
    &lt;linearGradient id="bgGradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%"&gt;
      &lt;stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#667eea;stop-opacity:1" /&gt;
      &lt;stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#764ba2;stop-opacity:1" /&gt;
    &lt;/linearGradient&gt;
  &lt;/defs&gt;
  &lt;circle cx="50" cy="50" r="48" fill="url(#bgGradient)" stroke="#ffffff" stroke-width="4"/&gt;
  &lt;text x="28" y="68" font-family="Roboto, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="42" font-weight="700" fill="#ffffff" text-anchor="middle"&gt;S&lt;/text&gt;
  &lt;text x="72" y="68" font-family="Roboto, system-ui, sans-serif" font-size="42" font-weight="700" fill="#ffffff" text-anchor="middle"&gt;L&lt;/text&gt;
&lt;/svg&gt;



Multiple Sizes Available:

Standard: favicon-sl.svg (100x100)
Small: favicon-16.svg (16x16)
Medium: favicon-32.svg (32x32)
